title: Drawing, "End Table, Round"
medium: Graphite on tracing paper, ruled border in graphite
markings: Stamp in black ink at lower left: DONALD DESKEY/ 501 MADISON AVENUE/ NEW YORK CITY
inscribed: Inscribed in graphite with dimensions; inscribed in graphite in lower right: SCALE 1 1/2"-1'0"/6315 [circled]; inscribed in red color pencil in lower right: P.
description: Perspective drawing for a small round end table in upper right, plan and elevation in lower left. Table has Bakelite (?) circular top, with four tubular metal legs. Feet for each leg bends at bottom and extends outward. Small tubular metal circle between four legs near ground.
